#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Service Manager</guilabel> module allows you to have an "
"overview of all plugins of the &kde; Daemon, also referred to as &kde; "
"Services. Generally, there are two types of service:"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Teenuste halduri</guilabel> moodul annab ülevaate kõigist &kde; "
"deemonite pluginatest, mida nimetatakse ka &kde; teenusteks. Üldiselt on "
"teenuseid kaht tüüpi:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Load-on-Demand Services"
msgstr "Soovi korral laaditavad teenused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a list of available &kde; services which will be started on demand. "
"They are only listed for convenience, as you cannot manipulate these "
"services."
msgstr ""
"See on nimekiri &kde; teenustest, mis käivitatakse soovi korral. Need "
"teenused on siin ainult mugavuse pärast, sest midagi seadistada siin ei saa."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup Services"
msgstr "Käivitamisel laaditavad teenused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shows all &kde; services that can be loaded on &kde; startup. Services "
"checked in the <guilabel>Use</guilabel> column will be invoked on next "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"See on nimekiri kõigist &kde; teenustest, mida on võimalik &kde; "
"käivitamisel laadida. Teenused, mille juures on veerus <guilabel>Kasutuses</"
"guilabel> märge, laaditakse järgmisel käivitamisel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful with deactivation of unknown services: some services are vital "
"for &kde;; do not deactivate services if you do not know what you are doing."
msgstr ""
"Ole tundmatute teenuste deaktiveerimisega ettevaatlik: mõned teenused on "
"&kde;le hädavajalikud. Seepärast ära lülita välja teenuseid, mille kohta sa "
"ei tea kindlalt, milleks see on mõeldud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the <guilabel>Status</guilabel> of a service, select it in the "
"list. Then you can use the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> and <guibutton>Stop</"
"guibutton> to change the status of a service from <guilabel>Not running</"
"guilabel> to <guilabel>Running</guilabel> and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Teenuse <guilabel>staatuse</guilabel> muutmiseks vali see loendis. Seejärel "
"kasuta nuppe <guibutton>Käivita</guibutton> ja <guibutton>Peata</guibutton> "
"teenuse staatuse muutmiseks staatusest <guilabel>Käivitamata</guilabel> "
"staatuseks <guilabel>Käivitatud</guilabel> ja vastupidi. "

